<HEAD>Police: U.S. Group Was To Receive Hostages' Pictures And Letter</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 2 grafs for grafs 14-15 pvs, `Police have ...' to UPDATE
with police ruling out Sutherland as man in photo; PICKS up 16th
pvs, `Anghessa, 44 ...' SUBS 3rd graf pvs, `Anghessa acted ...' to
